          <div class="ingredients">
            <h3>Ingredients</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>(makes 3/4 cup of dressing)</li>
              <li>1/2 cup mayo (see <a href="/5-minute-mayo">our 5-minute mayo recipe</a>) </li>
              <li>30g grated parmesan (1/2 â€“ 1 cup)</li>
              <li>1 teaspoon worcestershire sauce</li>
              <li>1 clove minced garlic</li>
              <li>2 anchovy fillets</li>
              <li>1/4 cup olive oil</li>
              <li>1/2 teaspoon black pepper</li>
              <li>1/4 teaspoon kosher salt</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="method">
            <h3>Method</h3>
            <ol>
              <li>Grate the parmesan.</li>
              <li>Combine all the ingredients (except the olive oil) in a jar slightly wider than your immersion blender.</li>
              <li>Place the immersion blender into the jar.</li>
              <li>pour in the olive oil.</li>
              <li>Blend for 15-30 seconds.</li>
              <li>Store in the fridge.Shake vigourously to revitalize it before using</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
